<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.8">
<l>curaraṟi varunilai viṇmutal muḻuvatum</l>
<l>varaṉmuta lāyavai muḻutuṇṭa paraparaṉ</l>
<l>puramoru mūṉṟerit tamararkku maṟiviyan</l>
<l>taraṉaya ṉeṉavula kaḻittamait tuḷaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Highest of the high who is the whole of those, being the first Cause</l>
<l>of the whole in heaven, of a state difficult to know for the gods,</l>
<l>igniting three cities with one [arrow], surpassing the knowledge of the immortals,</l>
<l>he exists, destroying [and] creating the world as Hara and Aja.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
